{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0a3ca89f3b","title":"在延安模范青年授奖大会上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"62f13fb1ee","index":0,"year":1939,"month":6,"day":6,"articleId":"0a3ca89f3b"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji13","name":"毛泽东全集第13卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji13.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji13":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f1b9dddcfa","type":"paragraph","text":"在延安模范青年授奖大会上的讲话口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"0a3ca89f3b"},{"id":"d1dfe78b38","type":"paragraph","text":"（1939年6月6日）青年应该把坚定正确的政治方向放在第一位，模范青年是代表中国老百姓，要一生代表他们。自己代表还不够，并且还要教训儿子，中国革命没有成功，要长期斗争，永远奋斗1939年，毛泽东和中共中央领导人在延安。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"0a3ca89f3b"},{"id":"5f4d17e779","type":"paragraph","text":"1939年6月6日，西北青救会在延安召开模范青年投奖大会，毛泽东为模范青年授奖并讲话。这是毛泽东在大会上讲话的一部分。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"0a3ca89f3b"}],"page":{"id":"254d32a3d7","publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"0a3ca89f3b","start":419,"end":419}}}},"__N_SSG":true}